301
00:18:44,139 --> 00:18:45,579
You say, no, no, pastor, you're wrong.

302
00:18:45,579 --> 00:18:47,500
My name is on the title of my car.

303
00:18:49,299 --> 00:18:51,179
I hope tonight that you can understand

304
00:18:51,179 --> 00:18:52,319
where I'm coming from,

305
00:18:52,319 --> 00:18:55,819
