00:19:28,299 --> 00:19:32,539
Let the kids be able to acknowledge and see

317
00:19:32,579 --> 00:19:36,500
and recognize, look at what God has done.

318
00:19:36,500 --> 00:19:39,139
Look at how God has provided.

319
00:19:39,139 --> 00:19:40,619
I shared this once before,

