00:20:23,559 --> 00:20:24,659
as we're in the front of the car,

341
00:20:24,659 --> 00:20:25,499
like, what are we gonna do?

342
00:20:25,499 --> 00:20:26,399
Like, this is tomorrow.

343
00:20:26,399 --> 00:20:28,399
Like, what are we gonna do here?

344
00:20:28,399 --> 00:20:30,159
